/**************************************************************/
/* d13design PHP site framework                               */
/* Created by Dave Waller © d13design 2011                    */
/**************************************************************/

This is a really simple MySQL based site framework, with templates,
written in PHP to support the build of a personal website.

There's nothing too special about it, it just makes my life a little bit
easier!

/**************************************************************/
/* Thanks and credits                                         */
/**************************************************************/

This framework uses a few libraries and resources created by others:

1. jQuery - http://www.jquery.com
2. Less - http://lesscss.org/
3. Twitter Bootstrap - http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/
4. Prettify - http://code.google.com/p/google-code-prettify/
5. Tipsy - http://plugins.jquery.com/project/tipsy
6. Dribbble - martin@mcbwebdesign.co.uk
7. nicEdit - http://www.nicedit.com/

